# EXISTING STRUCTURES

None

# ERROR TIPS

### Drill output blocked
- The drill at x=-14.0 y=-51.0 is frequently blocked because the belt at (-13.5, y=-49.5) is full. The agent repeatedly picks up the iron ore from the belt to unblock the drill. This indicates a bottleneck in the ore transportation system.
### Plate inserter waiting for source items
- The plate inserter at x=5.5 y=-59.5 is frequently waiting for source items, but the chest at x=4.5 y=-58.5 has 10 iron plates. This indicates an issue with the inserter configuration or the chest placement.
### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items
### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place a entity to a tile before attempting placing
